%h1 Badges Display

- @badges.each do |badge|
  %h3= link_to "#{badge.name}", badge_path(badge)
  = image_tag "badges/#{badge.image}"
  - if badge.claimcode && badge.claimcode != ""
    = render :partial => 'claim_code'
